citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:30 p.m. on
07-JUN-17.
The inspector spoke to an employee after arriving at the property. The employee stated that the licensee was not
home and was going to be unavailable for an inspection today.
